<<declare $AlexQuest = 0>>
<<if $AlexQuest < 1>>
    (There is a battery on the floor)
    <<stop>>
<<endif>>

<<if $AlexQuest == 1>>
    <<set $AlexQuest = 2>>
    You: Huh, this must be the battery that android is looking for, better take it back to him.
<<endif>>

<<if $AlexQuest > 2>>
<<endif>>

===
0 = not started quest
1 = started quest, no battery
2 = started quest, got battery
3 = finished quest